uiEntry.title: root
uiEntry.script:
local this = UIComponent(Address)
function ShowMenu(name) for i = 0, this:ChildCount() - 1 do local child = UIComponent(this:Find(i)) child:SetVisible(child:Id() == name) end end

state.title: NewState
state.stateText: Set during the Siege of Toulon, you will be given command of the French artillery battery. Aided by Napoleon's most trusted aide, you will learn the art of warfare in the defeat of the British army.

state.title: NewState
state.stateText: Take control of the French fleet at The Battle of Algeciras Bay, learning the rudiments of naval combat until you can tame both your enemies and the sea itself!

state.title: NewState
state.stateText: Set during Napoleon's youth, you will learn the basics of Total War's campaign game with the help of Louis Alexandre Berthier, Napoleon's most trusted staff officer. His help will guide you through the various trials that Napoleon encountered during his early life, culminating in the Siege of Toulon.
